  <oversight_info>
    <has_dmc>Yes</has_dmc>
  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This randomized cross-over study was designed to investigate the effects of legume enriched
      diet consumption on cardiovascular risk factors among first degree relatives of diabetic
      patients.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
