  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  subjects aged more than 30 years

          -  no history of chronic diseases

          -  no use of blood glucose lowering drugs be wiling to participate to study

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  do not follow study protocol

          -  incidence of chronic diseases during the study

          -  to start use of blood glucose lowering drugs or to change dose and type of current
             medications
      </textblock>
